{"word":"ἐπικαλέω","slug":"ἐπικαλέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐπιϰαλέω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐπί\">ἐπί</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:καλέω\">καλέω</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘give a name/nickname to’, <b>call, name, give a name/surname,</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> <b><a href='B:470 10:25'>Mt 10:25</a>; <a href='B:510 1:23'>Ac 1:23</a>; <a href='B:510 4:36'>4:36</a>; <a href='B:510 10:5'>10:5</a>; <a href='B:650 11:16'>Hb 11:16</a>; <a href='B:660 2:7'>Js 2:7</a>.</b> W. focus on proprietorship<b> <a href='B:510 15:17'>Ac 15:17</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘call upon for help/aid/intercession’, <b>invoke,</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ mid.\">mid.</a> <b><a href='B:510 2:21'>Ac 2:21</a>; <a href='B:520 10:12-14'>Ro 10:12-14</a>; <a href='B:530 1:2'>1 Cor 1:2</a>; <a href='B:620 2:22'>2 Ti 2:22</a>; <a href='B:670 1:17'>1 Pt 1:17</a>.</b> By extension as legal term <b>appeal <a href='B:510 25:11'>Ac 25:11</a></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ al.\">al.</a>; <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <b>call on as witness <a href='B:540 1:23'>2 Cor 1:23</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπικαθίζω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπικάλυμμα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}